OL,6,FA teenager has been jailed following
OL,7,Ftwo separate violent attacks in
OL,8,FPenrith.
OL,10,FThe first incident saw 19-year-old
OL,11,FReece Troy being involved in a group
OL,12,Fdisorder in the Burrowgate area, in
OL,13,FOctober 2023.
OL,15,FCarlisle Crown Court heard that words
OL,16,Fhad been exchanged inside the Pinny
OL,17,Fpub before trouble flared outside.
