OL,3,CTeenager jailed following two separate
OL,4,Cviolent attacks in town
OL,6,FThe victim recalled talking to Troy
OL,7,Fbut then nothing more as he was
OL,8,Fpunched and then had his head banged
OL,9,Fagainst a skip during an attack by
OL,10,Fseveral males.
OL,12,FHe lost consciousness and attended
OL,13,Fhospital where two forehead wounds
OL,14,Fwere glued, and a head injury stapled.
OL,16,FThe man ` a firefighter and self-
OL,17,Femployed joiner ` also suffered two
OL,18,Fblack eyes, facial pain, bruising and
OL,19,Finjuries to his shoulder and elbow.
