OL,3,CTeenager jailed following two separate
OL,4,Cviolent attacks in town
OL,6,FThis was only several hundred yards
OL,7,Ffrom the first incident, at the rear
OL,8,Fof Penrith's Devonshire Shopping
OL,9,FArcade.
OL,11,FHis victim was walking in that area
OL,12,Fwhen he met Troy, and was subjected to
OL,13,Fa serious sudden attack, resulting in
OL,14,Flosing consciousness. This left him
OL,15,Fwith a fractured eye socket, leg pain
OL,16,Fand cuts and bruises to his head and
OL,17,Farms.
OL,19,FTroy admitted his role in the attacks
OL,20,Fafterwards and pleaded guilty to two
OL,21,Fcounts of causing grievous bodily harm.
