OL,6,F"People are entitled to go to pubs and
OL,7,Fbe in town centres without the risk of
OL,8,Fbeing attacked by a violent thug."
OL,10,FTroy, previously of Eamont Mews,
OL,11,FPenrith, was sentenced to two-years in
OL,12,Fprison.
